name: Majestic animal
description: Cats have been side by side with humans for a long time. Therefore, many people like this furry animal. His cute and adorable behavior makes many people choose to maintain and become friends at home. The behavior of cats, especially kittens, is indeed funny, moreover a number of cat breeds also have unique shapes. Cats can be friends to dispel the feeling of loneliness at home, moreover these animals can be invited to play. Those who keep cats certainly feel the benefits of having a cat for mental health.
